snippet: With apologies to senior stars like Alabama's Jonathan Allen and Clemson's Deshaun Watson, none of college football's four remaining contenders for the national title made it this far without some help from the youngsters....
lead_paragraph: With apologies to senior stars like Alabama's Jonathan Allen and Clemson's Deshaun Watson, none of college football's four remaining contenders for the national title made it this far without some help from the youngsters.
